  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see whether HLA-mismatched donor cells infusion with
      chemotherapy (microtransplantation，MST) could increase complete remission (CR) and improve
      survival in older patients with acute myeloid leukemia (AML)，the investigators conducted a
      prospective, multicenter clinical trial of HLA-mismatched MST to estimate outcomes and
      toxicities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
